# Version 2.0 — Implementation Plan
## Customs Revenue & Trade Volume Prediction Analytics Platform

---

## Goal

Evolve the V1 portfolio demo into a **functional, intelligent analytics platform** that can:
1. **Predict** revenue and trade trends using ML models
2. **Interact** via natural language queries (chat-based analytics)
3. **Simulate** policy scenarios with real calculations
4. **Scale** with production-grade infrastructure
5. **Visualize** with a live web dashboard (replacing static Power BI)

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **V1 remains frozen.** V2 lives in a new directory (`customs-analytics-v2/`) under the same repo, inheriting architecture patterns but operating independently. V1 is the "before", V2 is the "after" — a compelling progression for any portfolio review.

---

## User Review Required

> [!WARNING]
> **Key Decisions Needed Before Building:**
> 1. **Scope:** Should we build all 5 phases, or start with a specific subset (e.g., just forecasting + web dashboard)?
> 2. **Web Framework:** Next.js (React) for the dashboard, or keep it simple with a single-page Vite app?
> 3. **ML Depth:** Simple statistical models (moving average, ARIMA) or also include Prophet/scikit-learn?
> 4. **LLM Integration:** Do you want a chat interface that queries the data via natural language? If yes, which LLM provider to target?
> 5. **Location:** Build V2 in `e:\Revenue_TradeVolumePrediction\bold\customs-analytics-v2/` as a sibling to the V1 project, or as a subdirectory in V1?

---

## What Changes from V1 → V2

| Dimension | V1 (Frozen) | V2 (New) |
|-----------|-------------|----------|
| **Purpose** | Portfolio demo | Functional analytics tool |
| **Data** | Static 50K synthetic records | 500K+ with seasonal patterns |
| **API** | 13 GET-only endpoints | 30+ endpoints (REST + WebSocket) |
| **Frontend** | Power BI (static) | Live web dashboard (React/Vite) |
| **ML/AI** | None | Revenue forecasting, anomaly detection |
| **Chat** | None | NLP query interface |
| **Scenarios** | Documented only | Interactive simulation engine |
| **Excise Tax** | Stub (returns 0) | Full implementation |
| **Auth** | None | API key + role-based access |
| **Deployment** | docker-compose (empty) | Working docker-compose + CI |
| **Tests** | Empty directories | Actual pytest test suite |

