## Execution Order

| Order | Phase | What Gets Built | Days |
|-------|-------|-----------------|------|
| 1 | **Foundation** | Working DB + API + Docker + 500K data | 2-3 |
| 2 | **Forecasting** | ML models + anomaly detection + full excise | 2-3 |
| 3 | **Scenarios** | Interactive policy simulation engine | 1-2 |
| 4 | **Dashboard** | React web app with all visualizations | 3-4 |
| 5 | **Chat** *(optional)* | NLP query interface | 2-3 |
| | **Total** | | **10-15 days** |

