## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
```bash
# Run full test suite
pytest tests/ -v

# Test API endpoints
pytest tests/test_api.py -v

# Test forecasting models
pytest tests/test_forecast.py -v

# Test scenario engine
pytest tests/test_scenarios.py -v
```

### Manual Verification
- Spin up `docker-compose up` and verify all services start
- Hit API docs at `http://localhost:8000/docs` — verify all endpoints
- Open dashboard at `http://localhost:3000` — verify all pages render
- Run a forecast and verify the prediction chart renders with confidence bands
- Run a scenario simulation and verify before/after comparison
- Browser test: navigate through all 5 dashboard pages

